  - scene: {fileID: 102900000, guid: 8c9cfa26abfee488c85f1582747f6a02, type: 3}
    sceneName: Level 1 - Fields of Redemption
    displayName: Fields of Redemption
    label: Level 1
    description: Once a peaceful meadow, now a scarred labyrinth of boulders and
      ancient stumps. The striking crimson poppies are said to spring only from the
      blood of fallen warriors, marking the treacherous passes where countless have
      perished.
    icon: {fileID: -9037230261874542816, guid: 8eb2610bb82e2b841bce6d8d1ec09b65, type: 3}
